# openvm-zorch runtime dependencies.
#
# Pulled from the Fractalyze package index alongside upstream PyPI:
#   pip install -r requirements.in \
#     --extra-index-url https://fractalyze.github.io/pypi/simple/
#
# frx/frxlib is the Fractalyze JAX distribution (Field, Ring Accelerated).
# The distribution NAME must track whatever the `zorch` pin in MODULE.bazel
# depends on; only the versions may skew. `zk-dtypes` moves with frx.
# Why the name is the load-bearing half: docs/development.md, "Dependency on
# zorch".
